title: NFL: Steelers vs. Giants
description: This is a market on the outcome of the NFL game between the Pittsburgh Steelers and the New York Giants.

markets.question: Will the Steelers beat the Giants by 6 or more points?
markets.description:

This market will resolve to “Steelers” if the Pittsburgh Steelers win their game against the New York Giants by 6 or more points.

title: Scorigami in NFL Week 8?
description:

This market will resolve to "Yes" if at least one NFL Scorigami occurs during Week 8 of the 2024-25 NFL Season. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".
